entries.journal_entry_description: A frantic request came in from the mountains of Naboo for a doctor. Head out to Naboo and help the family there.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: There's a serious medical situation on Naboo. A family that is living in the relative wilderness of Naboo has been attacked by a number of feral creatures. Several of the family members need tending.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You got a message from Billingsly: There's a serious medical situation on Naboo. A family that is living in the relative wilderness of Naboo has been attacked by a number of feral creatures. Several of the family members need tending.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Zaprin family has a small estate in the mountains of Naboo. Their home has been surrounded by sick animals and they need help.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Talk to Larence Zaprin and find out which of his family members needs tending.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Talk to Mia Zaprin and tend to her illness.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Mia's infection does not appear to react to the treatment. Collect 6 blood samples from the creatures outside to try to make an antidote.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Now that you have an anti-toxin, administer it to Mia and explain the possible side effects.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Talk to Mia and Administer the Antitoxin
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Now that you have an anti-toxin, administer it to Jowres and explain the possible side effects.
entries.task07_journal_entry_title: Talk to Jowres and Administer the Antitoxin
entries.task09_comm_message_text: Very good. You saved these people's lives. Don't forget to collect your deserved payment from Larence.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Very good. You saved these people's lives. Don't forget to collect your deserved payment from Larence.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Larence asked for a medic to make a house call. It's time to collect your fee.
